original: Landervik, Karl Ivar Hultin, komminister, Ingelstad, f. 12/5/10 i Vetlanda. G. 39 m. Ingegerd Eckerberg. Barn: Bengt f. 40, Sven 41, Alf 44, Eva 45. — Stud:ex. i Lund 29, teol. fil. ex. 30, teol. kand. o. prakt. teol. prov 34, prästv. f. Växjö stift 35. Past :adj. i Stockaryd 35, i Hovmantorp 36 o. i Tofteryd 38, v. kommin. i Oskarshamn 39, assist, sjöm. :pastor i Danzig 37-38, kommin. i Ö. Torsås sed. 40. Omb. f. Sv. kyrkans sjömansv :styr. o. f. Växjö stiftsråd, scoutled. Riksantikv. omib. FMM, Pro benignitatc humana.
translated: Landervik, Karl Ivar Hultin, curate, Ingelstad, b. 12/5/10 in Vetlanda. Married in 1939 to Ingegerd Eckerberg. Children: Bengt b. 1940, Sven b. 1941, Alf b. 1944, Eva b. 1945. — Education: graduated Lund 1929, Bachelor of Theology 1930, theological candidate and practical theological examination 1934, ordained priest in Växjö diocese in 1935. Pastoral assistant in Stockaryd 1935, Hovmantorp 1936, and Tofteryd 1938, temporary curate in Oskarshamn 1939, assistant ship chaplain in Danzig 1937-1938, curate in Ö. Torsås since 1940. Representative for the Swedish Church's Seamen's Welfare Board and Växjö Diocesan Board, scout leader, delegate for the National Heritage Board. Pro benignitatc humana.
